WEBVTT

00:08.175 --> 00:09.909
Someone's alive in here.

00:09.943 --> 00:11.539
You just can't help yourself, can you?

00:11.539 --> 00:12.665
Saving everyone.

00:12.699 --> 00:14.775
You want me to go and tell my CO

00:14.809 --> 00:16.143
to hail a UNN admiral

00:16.177 --> 00:17.644
in the middle of a war?

00:17.679 --> 00:18.779
Yes, exactly.

00:18.813 --> 00:19.980
So what is this thing

00:20.014 --> 00:21.348
that you want me to show them?

00:21.382 --> 00:23.784
Time is short, and I'll be brief.

00:23.818 --> 00:24.985
Are the prisoners secured?

00:25.019 --> 00:26.553
We have them in the med bay.

00:26.587 --> 00:28.488
What really happened on that ship?

00:28.523 --> 00:30.891
This war was built on a lie.

00:30.925 --> 00:32.558
Are you going to do something about it?

00:32.593 --> 00:33.961
I'm relieving you of command.

00:33.995 --> 00:35.562
The "Agatha King" is now mine.

00:35.596 --> 00:37.965
Melas has learned to live
without a father.

00:37.999 --> 00:40.000
We don't need you anymore.

00:40.034 --> 00:41.368
Fire!

00:41.402 --> 00:44.137
You guys fought one of
those things and won?

00:44.172 --> 00:47.107
All hybrid pods are ready for transfer.

00:48.443 --> 00:49.309
Whoa!

00:49.344 --> 00:50.377
Katoa, come on!

00:50.411 --> 00:52.012
I want to talk to Katoa.

00:52.046 --> 00:54.314
Disassembly reveals useful pathways.

00:54.349 --> 00:56.750
The boy is talking to the rest of

00:56.784 --> 00:58.218
the Protomolecule infestations.

00:58.252 --> 01:03.991
He's the key to everything.

